<font color="gray" size="4">Where's my pants?</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uatnastherogue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Atnas the Rogue</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/6/01 5:54:01 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yeah, park her over there please</span><hr size=1> The problem with No-Drop items is that it makes a dis-proportional amount of that item on the server you move to.<br>
